## Technical stuff

multiple seperate jobs:
* fetch new torrents & put into sqlite
* monitor torrents
* build overview
* offere api like interface


### there are a few ways to find seeder/peers
* DHT/PEX
* from trackers
	* TCP/HTTP
	* UDP/Infowire   https://www.bittorrent.org/beps/bep_0015.html
* LSD

